item.title: CVE-2022-36833|2024-08-03T10:14:28.496Z -- samsung%20mobile -- game%20optimizing%20service
item.description: Improper Privilege Management vulnerability in Game Optimizing Service prior to versions 3.3.04.0 in Android 10, and 3.5.04.8 in Android 11 and above allows local attacker to execute hidden function for developer by changing package name.
